{"tid":2339014,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[純學術討論] 香港人需唔需要為抗疫而律己  例如避免出街，減少群聚等","createTime":"2020-12-24T10:46:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-24T18:47:01.000Z","uid":387680,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2c314e495a05c9f8bb1915a0885b27a1777dad5a","tid":2339014,"uid":387680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:46:46.000Z","msg":"自武漢肺炎爆發差唔多一年，普遍專家認為社交距離嘅限制會有效阻止疫情傳播，<br />\n甚至外國有地區會封城同宵禁去限制市民出入自由。<br />\n<br />\n香港雖然暫時冇超大規模爆發，但係都出現唔少因為冇保持社交距離嘅個案同對應群組，<br />\n例如火鍋家庭，跳老舞，叫雞襟兄弟群組。（先忽略政府唔撚封關而引致非本地感染個案）<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\">如題，你覺得市民本身需唔需要為抗疫承擔一定義務而自我限制自由呢？</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：需要，我會盡力唔去街唔聚會減少社交，就算政府幾咁抗疫不力，都應該做好自身。如果因為我一時大意而令自己或者身邊人染疫，我都有責任。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：不了，我喜歡點做係我自由，出街戴口罩就得啦，就算瀨咗嘢都有得醫，驚閪。<br />\n生日就一定要去酒店慶祝，放假就一定要行山露營，定律嚟咖嘛！"},{"pid":"e101fdce643a897c890f124edf24ae78d895f7d1","tid":2339014,"uid":233905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:55:14.000Z","msg":"就算點努力港共都係會放啲感染者入嚟<br />\n四次都係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁辛苦有咩意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有只准返工不准娛樂？一層幾廿人嘅Office一定比幾個人gathering安全啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72199c3df7c6ef3e2282341db154a1d41d1c2484","tid":2339014,"uid":37715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:56:09.000Z","msg":"一早叫封關唔封<br />\n口罩戴晒又WFH<br />\n回落左啦又開大陸免檢疫pump返高條數<br />\n有咩咩群組都拎飲食業開刀先<br />\n學又停d唔停d<br />\n垃圾港共都係借疫情控制群眾姐<br />\n<br />\n我地就盡晒義務架啦政府無作為又屈9市民外出<br />\n我諗唔到有咩責任要聽佢支笛<br />\n病死咪病死爛命一條 好過我地做埋d無用既防疫措施"},{"pid":"1b80d4f5beb1e635883be62e6039aa0ae4b42e5d","tid":2339014,"uid":377064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T10:57:58.000Z","msg":"喺香港，自律唔代表會做到成功防疫"},{"pid":"4c99bd8d83626939f9deb49df3169c1d9645f7c9","tid":2339014,"uid":387680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T11:06:00.000Z","msg":"To rephrase the question: <br />\nDuring Covid19 pandemic, is social distancing a form of civic duty?"},{"pid":"0bd29a5a35304d212c41085d39f0185a20519009","tid":2339014,"uid":251026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T17:14:19.000Z","msg":"無徵狀基本無傳染, 無病徵就無需要防病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞mass testing係用嚟大量製造false positive case, 唔係為咗壓製病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nWHO Says Covid-19 Asymptomatic Transmission Is &lsquo;Very Rare&rsquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NQTBlbx1Xjs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNQTBlbx1Xjs&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGtxmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=3c2df488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NQTBlbx1Xjs</a>"},{"pid":"55b5f05e995449ef9c3d64b5e62d4e9b44d8a155","tid":2339014,"uid":74442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T18:47:01.000Z","msg":"屌，個仆街政府趕鬼入趕趕鬼出<br />\n自律有閪用咩"}]}